Class picture.ValueMapEntry 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----picture.ValueMapEntry
public class ValueMapEntry
extends Object
implements Parsable
This parses a value map entry of the form [.5 1.5] which means the piecewise linear function of the value map should map an input of .5 to an output of 1.5;

This code is (c) 1996 Leemon Baird <leemon@cs.cmu.edu>, http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~baird
